                "description": "The original, level residential section of Beverly Hills, north of Santa Monica Boulevard. Launched October 21, 1906 under the marketing slogan \"Between the City and the Sea,\" The Flats was Beverly Hills's founding residential vision \u2014 larger lots, wide tree-lined streets, and a mix of Spanish Colonial, Traditional, and Ranch-style homes favored by the old Hollywood elite. Today, modern revival estates and architect-driven celebrity compounds continue the neighborhood's century-long tradition of understated, land-rich luxury.",
