                "description": "Perhaps the most infamous address in American true crime, this was the site of the 1969 Manson Family murders. While the original house was demolished in 1994 and replaced with a new mansion (and a changed address to deter 'dark tourists'), the winding, narrow road still carries a heavy, somber legacy.",
