                "description": "A masterclass in California Mid-Century Modernism, this 1961 Richard Neutra-designed home features his signature walls of glass, terrazzo floors, and a seamless integration with the surrounding natural landscape. The home frames spectacular views stretching from downtown Los Angeles to the Pacific Ocean. Meticulously preserved and thoughtfully updated over the years, it recently changed hands in late 2025.",
