                "description": "A Whittier Boulevard staple that brought the authentic flavors of Ensenada to the Eastside. Famous for its crispy fish and shrimp tacos topped with a signature cream sauce, it stands as a testament to the diverse regional Mexican influences that have taken root in the neighborhood over the decades.",
