                "lng": -118.2843383,
                "address": "2703 S Hoover St, Los Angeles, CA 90007, USA",
                "description": "A masterpiece of the Queen Anne style, the Salisbury Residence is celebrated for its sweeping wrap-around porch and distinctive corner tower. This grand home captures the transitional spirit of the 1890s, blending refined Victorian details with a massive, commanding presence that remains one of the most photographed landmarks in the University Park neighborhood.",
