                "name": "Langer\u2019s Deli",
                "description": "An L.A. institution since 1947, Langer's is widely regarded as serving the best pastrami sandwich in the country. Located across from MacArthur Park, it has survived and thrived through the neighborhood's many transformations and remains a beloved anchor of Westlake.",
